title.Name: title
title.Value: Rope Climbing with No Legs - CoachTara Style

description.Name: description
description.Value: This is the first time since I was 10 years old and training in gymnastics that I have climbed a rope with just my hands.  I find that if I keep my arms bent and abdominal connected, by holding my knees up or in a pike position, I have a much smoother ride.  I love exploring all the things that my body can do.  CT
